Join live screenings and interact with creators
Engage with your favorite creators in exclusive
contract NFTTicketing { struct Ticket { uint256 id; address owner; bool isAvailable; } mapping(uint256 => Ticket) public tickets; function createTicket(uint256 id) public { tickets[id] = Ticket(id,
msg.sender, true); } function transferTicket(uint256 id, address newOwner) public { require(tickets[id].owner == msg.sender, "Not the ticket owner"); tickets[id].owner = newOwner; } }
